ght enemies in auto-battles. This way, you'll get rare resources to use to your advantage.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Liberate the world by lighting beacons and crafting your own army</h2>The world of Illuminaria was taken over by darkness. Unravel the story about what happened on the planet as you clean and liberate the five regions by lighting beacons and sending your armies of golems to attack.",
